                },
                "html": "Adventurers who fear encounters with cave worms might seek out a shuln and attempt to lure it along or magically compel it to aid in the fight to come, but the shuln\u02bcs stubborn personality makes such efforts difficult and unreliable. More often, acquiring the shuln\u02bcs saliva is an easier tactic, although the poison must be alchemically preserved if it is to be used as an injury poison, for this foul-smelling liquid breaks down quickly once it drools from the shuln\u2019s toothy maw."
            }
